      "type": "api_controller",
      "title": "Feature: calls (15 endpoints: DELETE, GET, POST)",
      "description": "Generate the COMPLETE NestJS module for 'calls' with ALL layers:\n- Controller (all 15 endpoints)\n- Service (business logic)\n- DTOs (request/response types)\n- Guards (JWT auth where needed)\n- Validators (input validation)\n- Module registration\n\nEndpoints:\n  POST /api/v1/calls \u2014 Create encrypted voice call session\n  GET /api/v1/calls \u2014 List calls\n  GET /api/v1/calls/{callId} \u2014 Get call details\n  POST /api/v1/calls/{callId}/participants \u2014 Add participant to call\n  DELETE /api/v1/calls/{callId}/participants/{participantId} \u2014 Remove participant from call\n  POST /api/v1/calls/{callId}/end \u2014 End call session\n  POST /api/v1/calls/{callId}/signaling/messages \u2014 Post WebRTC signaling message\n  GET /api/v1/calls/{callId}/signaling/messages \u2014 Fetch queued signaling messages\n  POST /api/v1/calls/{id}/join \u2014 Join a video call session\n  GET /api/v1/calls/{id} \u2014 Get video call session details\n  POST /api/v1/calls/{id}/end \u2014 End a video call session\n  POST /api/v1/calls/{callId}/screen-shares \u2014 Start screen sharing in a call\n  GET /api/v1/calls/{callId}/screen-shares \u2014 List screen sharing sessions in a call\n  DELETE /api/v1/calls/{callId}/screen-shares/{screenShareId} \u2014 Stop screen sharing in a call\n  POST /api/v1/calls/{callId}/reject \u2014 Reject an incoming call with a message",
